snippet.title: Backyard Baseball (1997) Longplay
snippet.description:
Backyard Baseball (1997) Longplay

Backyard Baseball is a Sports game for kids ages 5-10 created by Humongous Entertainment that teaches kids how to play Baseball. It is the first installment edition in the Backyard Baseball series, and the first game published as a part of the Backyard Sports (then called "Junior Sports") series overall.

Sorry for the terrible gameplay; have never played baseball before but I have watched it on TV. Just wanted to show off the game.
